takeaways.example:
AWS Step Functions or Temporal.io for orchestrating sample prep, data upload, and analysis steps:

{
  "SamplePrepAgent": "triggered by sample arrival",
  "AnalysisAgent": "runs on data upload event",
  "ReportingAgent": "generates report when analysis completes"
}

AWS Batch configuration for spot compute environments:

{
  "computeEnvironment": {
    "type": "SPOT",
    "minvCpus": 0,
    "maxvCpus": 100
  }
}

Celery task queue distributing analysis jobs:

{
  "task": "analyze_protein",
  "args": ["protein_id", "sample_id"]
}
